config files:
/etc/syslog.conf,system message logging
/etc/localtime,time zone data
/etc/ld.so.conf,dynamic loader search directories (shared libs .so)
/etc/vimrc,system-wide vim configuration
/etc/passwd,user account informations
/etc/group,group informations
/etc/sysconfig/ifconfig.*,network interface configuration
/etc/resolv.conf,domain name server list
/etc/hostname,computer name
/etc/hosts,hostnames static table
/etc/clock,hardware clock informations

kernel config:
